==English==

===Noun===
'''astroturfing''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#(''US politics'') Formal public relations projects that deliberately give the false impression that they are spontaneous and populist reactions.

===Etymology===
From [[Astroturf]]&reg;, as a pun on "grass roots", as astroturfing is intended to give the impression of grass-roots campaigns.

